on-colors\",\"children\":\"â†’\"}]]}]\n6:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"The Philosophy\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"TCG Times values \",[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"depth over hype\"}],\". You won't find pack-opening videos or speculative buylist spikes here. What you will find:\"]}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Thoughtful card theory and analysis\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Deckbuilding philosophy, not just decklists\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Cross-game insights that make you a better player everywhere\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Honest takes on game design, good and bad\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"Future Games\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"The card game space is evolving rapidly. As new games emerge that deserve serious attention â€” whether that's an innovative indie release or a major publisher's new entry â€” TCG Times will cover them. The goal is always the same: explore what makes each game interesting and help players get the most out of the hobby.\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"Get in Touch\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Have a theory you want to share? A game you think deserves more coverage? Reach out via the site's social links or submit your own content ideas.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Welcome to the table. ðŸƒ\"}]]}]\n7:[\"$\",\"$L8\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$9\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.MetadataOutlet\",\"children\":\"$@a\"}]}]\na:null\n"
